{"tid":1242298,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(粗口議員)  麥美娟: 堅持逃犯修例無問題","createTime":"2019-06-19T04:02:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T04:23:27.000Z","uid":134071,"like":5,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1dee83a07961cc66c74e2cac9b7dd6c5f54e77b2","tid":1242298,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:02:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1463741-20190619.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1463741-20190619.htm&d=Ye1L589%2FVCKAmP8JphB8dXJTAtm2oKGHsrawk8oVPbs%3D&h=c7a14c77\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1463741-20190619.htm&h=b1083403\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1463741-20190619.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n 麥美娟仍堅持修例無問題 只是社會氣氛不容討論<br />\n2019-06-19 HKT 10:33<br />\n<br />\n工聯會立法會議員麥美娟被問到會否接受特首林鄭月娥對建制派的道歉時表示，現時重點在於不在於接不接受她的道歉，而是修補社會上的撕裂，而建制派選情，亦不是她現時考慮的重點。<br />\n<br />\n麥美娟指出，建制派不存在盲目無條件支持特首，<strong>她認為條例本身無問題</strong>，若經過正常程序，即是經法案委員會討論是可以接受的，只是現時的社會氣氛不容許大家坐下來討論條例草案內容。"},{"pid":"d01bc4971df82b5a80d8c875789ccbf754351be8","tid":1242298,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:03:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">阻一阻你個post, 有d提議：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n除左要傾行動細節<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">我覺得星期五 既 主題 應該要集中加強 於</span> <br />\n<br />\n追究警察濫權濫用武力 ！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">先講建議：</span><br />\n1. 將依項命題提高到 同反送中 一樣高度/重要性！<br />\n2. 老土d, 黎緊日子整多d 中英示威大Banner關於警察濫權、濫用暴力、同醫館局私通 既問題，追究責任！<br />\n3. 議員都應該要有共識去追究依個問題<br />\n4. 加強各種文宣。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">原因：</span><br />\n<br />\n關於行動主題，我地要識得運用火種<br />\n將香港人團怒火keep住燒：<br />\n<br />\n無錯，撤回係未達成，但人人都知個問題，團火已經係白熱化，所以口號照叫，但唔好只集中於依個命題；<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無錯，明日大嶼/雙普選/國歌法都係係大問題，但現實就係依幾個議題好難吸引到大多數市民，太新、太遠，我地可以將佢地加插入我地既討論，但好難成為民意大爆發既火種，只可以乘住其他議題去帶出。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相反地，警察醫館局資料互通、差佬亂打青年人,和平示威者,女示威者、監警會無呀老虎，依d都係實實在在最令市民嬲既議題，亦都係國際社會既人權關注重點，我地一定要將依個命題加強到同反送中一樣高度！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40400491dac80189b9669c1da57f2e0a5d709ca5","tid":1242298,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:06:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8422c392140a31bd945a74aeb070ff6b8a182d00","tid":1242298,"uid":14918,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:09:19.000Z","msg":"再討論也可以<br />\n香港已經患有共癌, 癌細胞仲擴散到各界<br />\n要等外國制裁做下化療電療 消下毒先得<br />\n其實醫番好都周身傷, 病人安樂死也好"},{"pid":"b292b50c52c81c6e9232f2bcf3da7c98400484b6","tid":1242298,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:22:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79a27ccf6f1149d68d156ded482486fc8582aeee","tid":1242298,"uid":116289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,